PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE I TO THE YUKON SURFACE RIGHTS BOARD ACT - which adds the name of the Ta'an Kwach'an Council to the lists of Yukon First Nations set out in Parts I and II of Schedule I to the Act who have entered into both Land Claim and Self-Government Agreements with Canada and the Government of the Yukon Territory.
